            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股偏軟  深股報跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後偏軟，滬股近持平深股跌，兩市合計成交12717.44億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230629_FI_A股_9_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指全日收報3402點，升0.34點或0.01%，今早以3397點開市，跌4點或0.13%，早段低見3388，跌14點或0.41%，為全日低位，隨即節節向上，轉跌為升，最高見3408點，升6點0.18%，為全日高位，午後波幅不超過上午。全日成交5016.25億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日報10234點，跌11點或0.11%，今早開市報10208點，亦跌37點或0.37%。最低見10182，跌64點或0.62%，為全日低位，最高見10263，升17點或0.17%，為全日高位，成交7701.44億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數全日跌2點或0.06%，報3892點，今早跌9點或0.23%，開報3885點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日報2067，升5點或0.26%，今早開市報2057點，跌4點或0.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004645-a%e8%82%a1%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%a0%b1%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-12 15:15:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "螞蟻據報擬在香港及新加坡申請穩定幣牌照",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》引述消息人士指，螞蟻國際正部署在香港及新加坡申請穩定幣牌照，以加強跨境支付及資金管理服務。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231228_FI_source_licensed_穩定幣1_shutterstock_704.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231228_FI_source_licensed_穩定幣1_shutterstock_704.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，螞蟻計畫在香港《穩定幣條例》於8月生效後，立即申請穩定幣發行牌照。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)旗下螞蟻集團近年逐漸增加在港投資，早前才斥28億元收購耀才證券(01428)50.55%，並依例提全面收購，但明言擬維持耀才的上市地位。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15004551-%e8%9e%9e%e8%9f%bb%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e6%93%ac%e5%9c%a8%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%8a%e6%96%b0%e5%8a%a0%e5%9d%a1%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e7%a9%a9%e5%ae%9a%e5%b9%a3%e7%89%8c%e7%85%a7",
